     C*
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADD0         WKASI   72
   E1C                     END
      *
     C                     Z-ADDISRYO     WSRYO   60
      *
     C* CALUCULATE ONE PART TOTAL NET WEIGHT
     C* (UNIT WEIGHT * QTY)/1000*2.22
